*Added*
-Additional meta fields for ebooks: sub_series, order
-Added additional fields to edit form and added sub_series to list view
-Added feature to allow the cbz reader to navigate to the next issue, if one exists within the current series & sub-series and you are on the last page of the current issue.
*Changes*
-Modified the order option for db_handler and db_meta_handler to support arrays so that complex order clauses can be built. Does not currently support per column order directions.
*Fixes*
-Patched some faulty logic in db_handler and db_meta_handler.